SSL Certificates Update on APACHE ( Connect 7 ) 

New Certificates For 2026

chartiq.com          				- (Server Certificate)
DigiCertGlobalG2TLSRSASHA2562020CA1 - (Intermediate CA)
DigiCertGlobalRootG2                - (Root CA)
chartiq.key                         - (Private Key)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Pre Verification :

Confirm Current Certificate:
openssl x509 -in /etc/apache2/ssl/2025/chartiq_com.crt -noout -dates

Expected:
notBefore=Jun 11 00:00:00 2025 GMT
notAfter=Jun 10 23:59:59 2026 GMT 
Record the current expiry date.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Verify CRT and KEY match

openssl rsa -noout -modulus -in chartiq.key | openssl md5
openssl x509 -noout -modulus -in chartiq.com | openssl md5

The MD5 hashes must be identical.


------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Recommended Deployment Steps
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Create 2026 SSL directory

sudo mkdir /etc/apache2/ssl/2026

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

3. Copy files

/etc/apache2/ssl/2026/

chartiq.com.crt                         -> chartiq_com.crt
DigiCertGlobalG2TLSRSASHA2562020CA1.crt -> DigiCertCA.crt
DigiCertGlobalRootG2.crt                -> TrustedRoot.crt
chartiq.key                             -> chartiq.key

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

4. Verify New Directory
 
ls -l /etc/apache2/ssl/2026

Should look similar to:
chartiq_com.crt
chartiq.key
DigiCertCA.crt
TrustedRoot.crt
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

5. Backup Current Configs

cd /etc/apache2/sites-available/

cp -p rob.chartiq.com.conf rob.chartiq.com.conf.2025bak
cp -p license.chartiq.com-le-ssl.conf license.chartiq.com-le-ssl.conf.2025bak
cp -p devservices.chartiq.com-ssl.conf devservices.chartiq.com-ssl.conf.2025bak
cp -p 000-default.conf 000-default.conf.2025bak
cp -p monit.chartiq.com.conf monit.chartiq.com.conf.2025bak


//or// Optional, safe side can take the back-up

tar -czvf /tmp/sites-available-before-2026.tar.gz /etc/apache2/sites-available ( Optional )
tar -czvf /tmp/ssl2025_backup.tar.gz /etc/apache2/ssl/2025  ( Optional )
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	  
6. Update SSL Paths

In these files:

rob.chartiq.com.conf
license.chartiq.com-le-ssl.conf
devservices.chartiq.com-ssl.conf
000-default.conf
monit.chartiq.com.conf

change:
From  /ssl/2025/

To  /ssl/2026/

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

7. Confirm All References

grep -Ri "ssl/2026" /etc/apache2/sites-available

Also cross verify:
grep -Ri "ssl/2025" /etc/apache2/sites-available

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

8. Validate Apache

apachectl configtest

Expected:
Syntax OK

Note: Do not restart if this fails.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

9. Restart Apache

systemctl restart apache2
service apache2 restart


Verify Service

ps -ef | grep apache2

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

10. Verify New Certificate

openssl s_client \
-connect rob.chartiq.com:443 \
-servername rob.chartiq.com \
</dev/null 2>/dev/null | openssl x509 -noout -dates

This Confirm the new expiration date.

